WITH FORCIBLE INTERCOURSE.

31:05.564 --> 31:08.267
BUT NO FOREIGN DNA
ON HER PERSON.

31:08.300 --> 31:09.501
- WELL, SHE SHOWERED.

31:09.535 --> 31:11.503
SO IT WAS WORTH
A SHOT.

31:11.537 --> 31:14.040
- I DID FIND MICHAEL WEDMORE'S
DNA ON THE CUP.

31:14.073 --> 31:15.074
ANYTHING ON THE BED?

31:15.107 --> 31:18.044
- YES, FRESH SEMEN
WITHIN 24 HOURS OF THE RAPE.

