WAS IT?

31:48.240 --> 31:49.275
- I DON'T REMEMBER
HIS NAME.

31:49.308 --> 31:52.178
IT WAS JUST
A ONE-NIGHT STAND.

31:52.211 --> 31:54.180
- WAS IT THE GUY
FROM THE BAR?

31:54.213 --> 31:56.115
- YES.

31:56.148 --> 31:58.317
- PLEASE DON'T TELL ME
HE'S BLACK.

31:58.350 --> 32:01.120
- YEAH.

32:01.153 --> 32:03.022
- DID YOU TAKE
THE ELEVATOR?

32:03.055 --> 32:07.126
- YEAH.

32:10.529 --> 32:13.165
- WE SPECIFICALLY ASKED YOU
ABOUT THIS.

32:13.199 --> 32:16.168
- I'VE NEVER PICKED ANYONE UP
AT A BAR BEFORE.

32:16.202 --> 32:18.304
I JUST THOUGHT THAT
IT MIGHT LOOK BAD.

32:18.337 --> 32:20.372
