YOU LIED TO US.

32:20.406 --> 32:23.142
- YOU KNOW WHAT?
STUDYING MUSIC IS HARD.

32:23.175 --> 32:25.377
YOU'RE ALONE,
YOU'RE PRACTICING ALL THE TIME.

32:25.411 --> 32:28.047
