- ELLIS IS GONNA TRY TO USE
THE OTHER MAN'S DNA

32:40.492 --> 32:42.228
TO CREATE
REASONABLE DOUBT.

32:42.261 --> 32:44.563
- I WAS JUST
TRYING TO BE

32:44.596 --> 32:48.534
A NORMAL COLLEGE KID
FOR ONCE.

32:48.567 --> 32:51.237
[scoffs]
SO WHAT?

32:51.270 --> 32:54.073
DOES THIS MEAN THAT
YOU DROP THE CASE?

32:54.106 --> 32:57.009
- NO, HE STILL RAPED YOU
AT GUNPOINT.

32:57.043 --> 32:59.745
- BUT YOU'RE SAYING
THE JURY WON'T BELIEVE ME.

32:59.778 --> 33:02.981
- JUST TELL THE TRUTH,
AND LET ME WORRY ABOUT THE REST.

33:06.152 --> 33:09.088
- ON A SUNNY AFTERNOON,
SARAH WALSH

33:09.121 --> 33:12.358
ENTERED HER APARTMENT
WITH HER GROCERIES.

33:12.391 --> 33:14.526
WHEN SHE TURNED TO CLOSE
HER FRONT DOOR,

33:14.560 --> 33:18.164
SHE FOUND THE DEFENDANT
POINTING A GUN AT HER.

33:18.197 --> 33:21.033
- DO YOU OWN A GUN?
- NO.

33:21.067 --> 33:22.268
- HOW DO YOU EXPLAIN
THE GUN

33:22.301 --> 33:24.236
THE DETECTIVES ALLEGEDLY FOUND
IN YOUR GIRLFRIEND'S APARTMENT?

33:24.270 --> 33:27.239
- ALL I KNOW IS, WHILE
ONE OFFICER HELD ME AT GUNPOINT,

33:27.273 --> 33:29.775
THE OTHER ONE PULLS
THIS GUN OUT OF NOWHERE

33:29.808 --> 33:31.243
AND SAYS,
"YOU SHOULDN'T HAVE RUN."

33:31.277 --> 33:33.779
- HAD YOU EVER SEEN
THAT GUN BEFORE?

33:33.812 --> 33:35.814
- NO. LOOK,
I MAY BE A POT DEALER,

33:35.847 --> 33:38.317
BUT THAT'S JUST SO I CAN PROVIDE
FOR MY FAMILY.

33:38.350 --> 33:39.485
I DEAL SMALL QUANTITIES.

33:39.518 --> 33:41.287
MISDEMEANORS.

33:41.320 --> 33:44.223
EVERYBODY KNOWS
A GUN IS A FELONY.

33:44.256 --> 33:47.326
- MR. WEDMORE HELD HER
AT GUNPOINT.

33:47.359 --> 33:50.096
HE LOCKED THE DOOR.

33:50.129 --> 33:51.263
SHE OFFERED HIM A BEER,

33:51.297 --> 33:54.166
HOPING THAT THE KINDNESS
WOULD KEEP HIM FROM KILLING HER.

33:54.200 --> 33:57.369
- WERE YOU IN
MISS WALSH'S APARTMENT?

33:57.403 --> 33:59.505
- YES. I HELPED HER
IN WITH HER GROCERIES.

33:59.538 --> 34:02.141
SHE OFFERED ME
A BEER.

34:02.174 --> 34:05.811
MY MOTHER ALWAYS TOLD ME
TO STAY AWAY FROM WHITE WOMEN.

34:05.844 --> 34:08.147
BUT SHE SEEMED NICE,
SO I TOOK IT.

34:08.180 --> 34:08.980
- HE WOULDN'T LEAVE.

34:09.014 --> 34:12.351
WITH THE GUN
STILL POINTED AT HER,

34:12.384 --> 34:15.221
SHE OFFERED HIM MONEY.

34:15.254 --> 34:17.223
BUT THAT'S NOT
WHAT HE WANTED.

34:17.256 --> 34:18.757
- AFTER SHE INVITED YOU
INTO HER APARTMENT,

34:18.790 --> 34:21.560
OFFERED YOU A BEER,
WHAT HAPPENED NEXT?

34:21.593 --> 34:23.429
- I WANTED TO GO.

34:23.462 --> 34:25.531
I HAD TO GET BACK
TO WORK.

34:25.564 --> 34:27.099
THEN SHE STARTED
ACTING WEIRD.

34:27.133 --> 34:28.534
- HOW SO?

34:28.567 --> 34:31.237
- SHE ASKED ME IF I WANTED
TO HAVE SEX WITH HER.

34:31.270 --> 34:34.506
- HE TOLD HER
TO UNDRESS

34:34.540 --> 34:37.476
AND LAY
ON THE BED.

34:37.509 --> 34:42.214
SARAH,
FEARING FOR HER LIFE,

34:42.248 --> 34:45.117
DID AS SHE WAS TOLD.

34:45.151 --> 34:46.285
- DID YOU HAVE SEX
WITH HER?

34:46.318 --> 34:49.321
- NO.
I LOVE MY GIRLFRIEND.

34:54.393 --> 34:56.562
- YOU OKAY?

34:56.595 --> 35:00.766
- YOUR FRIEND ELLIS TRIED TO
SHAKE MY STORY ON THE GUN.

35:00.799 --> 35:01.967
HE THREW IT
UNDER THE COUCH.

35:02.000 --> 35:04.136
THERE WAS A KID IN THE HOUSE.
WHAT WAS I SUPPOSED TO DO?

35:04.170 --> 35:06.238
- I GET IT. WE'VE ALL BEEN
THERE, HEAT OF THE MOMENT.

35:06.272 --> 35:08.774
NEXT TIME, CUFF HIM,
SEAL THE ROOM,

35:08.807 --> 35:11.810
AND WAIT FOR A WARRANT,
OKAY?

35:14.813 --> 35:16.915
- MISS WALSH, IS THIS YOU WITH
MY CLIENT IN YOUR ELEVATOR?

35:16.948 --> 35:18.584
- YES.

35:18.617 --> 35:21.187
- AND YOU CLAIMED YOU'VE NEVER
MET MY CLIENT BEFORE?

35:21.220 --> 35:22.053
- THAT'S CORRECT.

35:22.087 --> 35:23.322
- ARE YOU SURE?
YOU LOOK SO FRIENDLY.

35:23.355 --> 35:25.224
- OBJECTION.
- WITHDRAWN.

35:25.257 --> 35:26.925
AN HOUR LATER...

35:26.958 --> 35:29.195
