MY CLIENT LEAVING?

35:29.228 --> 35:30.429
- YES.

35:30.462 --> 35:33.199
- NO TORN CLOTHING, NO SIGNS
OF STRUGGLE. WOULD YOU AGREE?

35:33.232 --> 35:36.235
- YES.

35:43.342 --> 35:46.312
- AFTER MY CLIENT LEFT,
