35:46.345 --> 35:48.314
OR A FRIEND?
- AFTER HE RAPED ME, I--

35:48.347 --> 35:50.349
- YOU DIDN'T CALL ANYONE,
DID YOU?

35:50.382 --> 35:51.383
- NO.

35:51.417 --> 35:53.185
- NO. INSTEAD,
YOU WENT TO SCHOOL.

35:53.219 --> 35:54.786
YOU PERFORMED
A PIANO RECITAL.

35:54.820 --> 35:55.921
- I HAD TO
FOR THE GRADE--

35:55.954 --> 35:58.924
- AND YOU GOT AN "A."
IMPRESSIVE.

35:58.957 --> 36:01.260
CONSIDERING HOW LATE
YOU WERE OUT THE NIGHT BEFORE.

36:01.293 --> 36:02.861
3:00 A.M.

36:02.894 --> 36:05.897
DO YOU RECOGNIZE THIS MAN,
MISS WALSH?

36:08.300 --> 36:10.236
- YES.

36:10.269 --> 36:12.471
- DID YOU INVITE HIM
INTO YOUR APARTMENT?

36:19.245 --> 36:20.812
- YES.

36:20.846 --> 36:23.515
- AND YOU HAD SEX WITH HIM ON
YOUR BED THAT NIGHT, DID YOU?

36:23.549 --> 36:24.983
- YES.

36:25.016 --> 36:26.852
- IS IT POSSIBLE
THE INJURIES YOU SUSTAINED

36:26.885 --> 36:28.520
WERE FROM VIGOROUS SEX
WITH THIS MAN

36:28.554 --> 36:30.256
BEFORE YOU MET
MY CLIENT?

36:30.289 --> 36:32.324
- IT WASN'T ROUGH.

36:32.358 --> 36:33.825
