36:33.859 --> 36:36.828
- WOULD THIS MAN BE ABLE TO COME
FORWARD AND TESTIFY TO THAT?

36:40.031 --> 36:41.933
- NO.

36:41.967 --> 36:45.604
- AND WHY IS THAT?

36:45.637 --> 36:48.874
- I DON'T KNOW HIS NAME.

36:48.907 --> 36:50.876
- ON THE TAPE, HE LOOKS
VERY SIMILAR TO MY CLIENT.

36:50.909 --> 36:52.444
MID-20s, ATHLETIC BUILD,
BLACK.

36:52.478 --> 36:54.380
- OBJECTION, YOUR HONOR.
THE DEFENSE--

36:54.413 --> 36:57.015
- REPHRASE. IS IT SAFE TO SAY
YOU HAVE A TYPE, MISS WALSH?

36:57.048 --> 36:58.517
- WATCH YOURSELF,
MR. ELLIS.

36:58.550 --> 36:59.885
- WITHDRAWN.
MISS WALSH,

36:59.918 --> 37:01.987
WHY DID YOU WAIT SO LONG
TO FILE A POLICE REPORT?

37:02.020 --> 37:04.356
- BECAUSE I DIDN'T WANT
ANYONE TO KNOW.

37:04.390 --> 37:06.024
- ANYONE?

37:06.057 --> 37:10.462
YOU MEAN,
YOUR PARENTS?

37:10.496 --> 37:12.331
OR YOUR BOYFRIEND?

37:12.364 --> 37:13.399
- YES.

37:13.432 --> 37:15.967
- SO YOU DIDN'T WANT THEM
TO KNOW

37:16.001 --> 37:17.469
YOU WERE ALONE
WITH MY CLIENT,

37:17.503 --> 37:18.904
OR YOU DIDN'T WANT
TO LET THEM KNOW

37:18.937 --> 37:20.939
YOU WERE ALONE WITH SOME RANDOM
MAN THE NIGHT BEFORE?

37:20.972 --> 37:23.975
THE ONE WHO LEFT HIS SEMEN
ON YOUR SHEETS?

37:27.078 --> 37:30.282
WHICH IS IT,
MISS WALSH?

37:32.484 --> 37:35.421
TAKE YOUR TIME.

37:35.454 --> 37:38.457
IT IS CONFUSING.

37:44.996 --> 37:47.833
- LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,
THIS ISN'T 1970.

37:47.866 --> 37:49.835
IT'S 2011.

37:49.868 --> 37:51.837
AND YET YOU WOULDN'T KNOW IT
FROM THE WAY

37:51.870 --> 37:55.841
