VICTIM'S PERSONAL LIFE ON TRIAL.

37:55.874 --> 38:00.412
IT'S THE DEFENDANT'S ACTIONS
THAT MATTER HERE.

38:00.446 --> 38:03.081
NOW, HE ADMITS TO BEING
IN THE BUILDING

38:03.114 --> 38:06.017
BUT CLAIMS HE WAS ONLY THERE
TO DELIVER POT.

38:06.051 --> 38:10.088
HE ADMITS ENTERING
MISS WALSH'S APARTMENT

38:10.121 --> 38:12.891
BUT CLAIMS
HE JUST HAD A BEER.

38:12.924 --> 38:16.061
BUT WHAT
HE WON'T ADMIT

38:16.094 --> 38:19.465
IS THE HORRIBLE TRUTH...

38:19.498 --> 38:21.367
THAT IN LESS THAN
AN HOUR,

38:21.400 --> 38:25.404
AT GUNPOINT,

38:25.437 --> 38:28.440
HE IRREVOCABLY CHANGED
A YOUNG WOMAN'S LIFE.

38:36.982 --> 38:38.149
- MR. FOREMAN.

38:38.183 --> 38:40.886
IT IS MY UNDERSTANDING THAT
YOU HAVE COME TO A DECISION.

38:40.919 --> 38:43.321
- YES,
YOUR HONOR.

38:46.057 --> 38:48.093
ON THE CHARGE OF
CRIMINAL POSSESSION OF A WEAPON,

38:48.126 --> 38:49.428
WE FIND
THE DEFENDANT

38:49.461 --> 38:54.065
NOT GUILTY.

38:54.099 --> 38:55.567
ON THE CHARGE
OF RAPE,

38:55.601 --> 38:57.369
WE FIND THE DEFENDANT
NOT GUILTY.

39:00.439 --> 39:02.107
- YOU BLACK BASTARD!

39:02.140 --> 39:05.343
[gavel bangs]
- ORDER!

39:09.114 --> 39:12.584
- SARAH--
- DON'T!

39:12.618 --> 39:14.553
DON'T YOU DARE TELL ME THAT
THAT WAS WORTH IT.

39:14.586 --> 39:16.388
THAT WAS SO UGLY!

39:16.422 --> 39:18.957
- SARAH, YOU DIDN'T LET HIM
GET AWAY WITH IT.

39:18.990 --> 39:20.826
YOU ACCUSED HIM
IN PUBLIC--

39:20.859 --> 39:21.827
- SO WHAT?

39:21.860 --> 39:26.164
HE'S GOING HOME
WITH HIS FAMILY.

39:26.197 --> 39:29.100
I WOULD HAVE NEVER
LET ANYONE GO THROUGH THAT.

39:29.134 --> 39:31.136
- THAT'S TRUE, AND I KNOW THAT
THAT'S HOW YOU FEEL RIGHT NOW--

39:31.169 --> 39:32.838
- NO, YOU HAVE NO IDEA
HOW I FEEL!

39:32.871 --> 39:35.073
- SARAH,
LISTEN TO ME.

39:35.106 --> 39:38.410
SENDING HIM TO PRISON

39:38.444 --> 39:41.046
ISN'T GONNA HEAL YOU.

39:41.079 --> 39:45.116
HEALING BEGINS WHEN
SOMEONE BEARS WITNESS.

39:45.150 --> 39:48.019
I SAW YOU.

39:48.053 --> 39:52.491
I BELIEVE YOU.

39:52.524 --> 39:55.527
- COME ON, BABY.
LET'S GO.

40:00.131 --> 40:01.967
- CONGRATULATIONS.

40:02.000 --> 40:05.003
- THANK YOU.

40:16.147 --> 40:18.049
- [sighs]

40:20.952 --> 40:23.121
