FOR COMPANY.

40:23.154 --> 40:25.991
- BUT YOU GOT IT.

40:26.024 --> 40:28.894
- ARE YOU PROUD
OF YOURSELF?

40:28.927 --> 40:31.630
YOU BROUGHT UP
EVERY STEREOTYPE.

40:31.663 --> 40:34.065
YOU SHAMED THAT GIRL
ABOUT HER SEXUALITY.

40:34.099 --> 40:37.235
YOU SAID THAT IF A WHITE GIRL
IN THAT NEIGHBORHOOD CRIES RAPE,

40:37.268 --> 40:40.539
SHE MUST HAVE WANTED IT?
NICE WORK.

40:40.572 --> 40:43.041
- AND YOUR CASE?
THE I.D.?

40:43.074 --> 40:45.110
THE GUN YOUR PARTNER HEARD
SLIDE UNDER THE COUCH?

40:45.143 --> 40:46.845
NO DNA?

40:46.878 --> 40:49.548
IF MICHAEL WERE WHITE, THIS
NEVER WOULD'VE GONE TO TRIAL.

40:49.581 --> 40:50.982
- OH, WOW.

40:51.016 --> 40:53.018
YOU'RE STILL PLAYING
THE RACE CARD, HUH?

40:53.051 --> 40:57.055
- 84% OF THE YOUNG MEN IN NEW
YORK JAILS ARE BLACK AND LATINO.

40:57.088 --> 40:58.289
- HE RAPED HER!

40:58.323 --> 41:00.659
- SO SHE SAYS. WE DON'T KNOW.
NEITHER ONE OF US WAS THERE.

41:00.692 --> 41:03.228
THE ONLY THING WE CAN DO
IS BELIEVE OUR PEOPLE,

41:03.261 --> 41:05.497
