WITHOUT QUESTION.

41:05.531 --> 41:08.133
- SO THAT'S IT.

41:08.166 --> 41:12.070
YOU'RE A TRUE BELIEVER.

41:12.103 --> 41:14.005
- I AM.

41:14.039 --> 41:16.975
AND SO ARE YOU.

41:17.008 --> 41:18.910
- I JUST DO MY JOB.

41:18.944 --> 41:21.513
- LOOK, NOT EVERYONE
IN THE N.Y.P.D.

41:21.547 --> 41:22.981
IS LIKE YOU, DETECTIVE.

41:23.014 --> 41:24.616
I WISH THEY WERE.

41:24.650 --> 41:26.251
I COULD RETIRE.

41:26.284 --> 41:28.654
THIS JOB,
FIGHTING THIS HARD, IT--

41:28.687 --> 41:32.257
WIN OR LOSE,
IT COMES WITH A COST.

41:32.290 --> 41:38.063
WE BOTH KNOW THAT,
DON'T WE?

41:38.096 --> 41:39.531
- YOU KNOW,
I LOOK AT THE UNIS,

41:39.565 --> 41:40.999
ALL THESE KIDS
IN THE SQUAD ROOM,

41:41.032 --> 41:46.071
AND ALL
I CAN THINK OF

41:46.104 --> 41:48.039
IS I'M SO TIRED.

41:48.073 --> 41:51.276
- I GET IT.

41:51.309 --> 41:54.512
THIS IS WHAT HAPPENS
WHEN YOU LIVE FOR THE JOB.

41:59.017 --> 42:02.654
YOU NEED AN ESCAPE.

42:02.688 --> 42:04.856
I COACH MY DAUGHTER'S
SOFTBALL TEAM.

42:04.890 --> 42:07.893
- THAT MUST BE HELL
ON THE UMP.

42:09.961 --> 42:12.998
- WHY DON'T YOU COME OUT
AND CATCH A GAME?

42:13.031 --> 42:15.601
- I DO OKAY
ON MY OWN.

42:15.634 --> 42:18.637
- YOU SURE ABOUT THAT?
